'''Bakura''' is a character in ''[[Yu-Gi-Oh! Forbidden Memories]]''. This is a video game depiction of [[Ryo Bakura (manga)|Ryo Bakura]] from the [[Yu-Gi-Oh! (manga)|''Yu-Gi-Oh!'' manga]].

He appears in the present day events of the game, where he partakes in the tournament, however [[Yami Bakura (FMR)|Yami Bakura]] takes over and duels in his stead. After defeating Yami Bakura, [[Yugi (FMR)|Yugi]] uses the [[Millennium Item Card]] to get the [[Millennium Ring (Forbidden Memories)|Millennium Ring]], freeing Bakura from the Ring's influence.

